{"tid":97973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣今年國運求得下下籤 掛頭「聞仲西征遇十絕陣後逃」","createTime":"2017-01-28T05:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T12:18:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d262494621528b913b7e431546abaaa540e4008","tid":97973,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"命中「武則天坐天」的代天府　今年國運籤出爐<br />\n<br />\n2017/01/28 12:42&nbsp;22305<br />\n<br />\n（更新：新增解籤影片）<br />\n南鯤鯓代天府今天上午十一時舉辦國運籤活動，循古禮三跪九叩，連抽九支籤，終於擲出三聖杯，選定今年國運籤為掛頭「聞仲西征遇十絕陣後逃」的籤詩。<br />\n總幹事侯賢遜說，此為下下籤，四句掛尾分別為一重山、路又難、終不過、未得安，沒一句好話，但籤詩參考用，命運靠人改變，政府讓人走對的路，百姓同心協力，什麼艱難都能過。南鯤鯓代天府前年求國運籤「武則天坐天」，在大選前引發討論，有信眾直呼「金準！」。今年國運籤詩內容：「一重江水一重山，誰知此去路又難；任他改求終不過，是非到底未得安」。（王志弘／台南報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170128/640_d9b34181bfc34d3f02ea437d6715fd33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170128%2F640_d9b34181bfc34d3f02ea437d6715fd33.jpg&h=b81300d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170128/1045301/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170128%2F1045301%2F&d=0H4oW%2BgquIP99nIvOe5VJWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f7614686\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170128/1045301/</a><br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"9e54b2e470821a2b5f9b05ccbc4724439731b5a6","tid":97973,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0009075411cf6f2f7e8740b5c2bef6d65df17e2","tid":97973,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"下面個解先正<br />\n一係就不 一係就凶<br />\n囉一一個有，配個失字"},{"pid":"cf5c5f37a93d0c38e722a1b94dc63997cfb8ee0d","tid":97973,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:41:06.000Z"